                              "content": "The dark-mode counterpart of the Tiramisu system. Same Anton condensed display, Geist body, Inter uppercase eyebrows — re-tuned for OLED surfaces, deeper aubergines and teals, and a slightly hotter accent purple. Built for late-night roomie reconciliations after Big Bazaar runs.",
